{"type": "article", "id": 29172, "title": "由光原理打造的桌子", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-05T22:53:29Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607052205084L7kPyiOQXolVNBZ.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>当光线穿过穹顶的窗户，金色的光芒就会倾泻而下，虽然本身不可触摸但你可以通过它清楚地看到空气中飘浮的灰尘颗粒。跨领域设计师 <a href=\"http://www.meganlin-design.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Megan Lin</a> 就以自然光这种迷人的特质设计了名为 Gather Light 的家具组合，包括一个有倾斜角度的桌子和配套的吊灯，能够让人们与光一起互动。桌子的立柱与地面成 75 度斜角，桌面则被漆上了渐变的蓝色，旋转时颜色还会发生变化。当灯光或者阳光穿透玻璃时会在地上留下漂亮的颜色，Lin 希望通过这种形式让人感受到某个时刻的纯粹与美好，Gather Light 正是她 <a href=\"http://www.meganlin-design.com/bring-together/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bring Together</a> 冥想系列中的一部分。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607052241487gxWh6LnAo8ZqJRe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.591687\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160705224148780yTMEfrbHVtRq3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646699\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160705224149ZWPAskfua7UXORCS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646699\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160705224149vpsWakrueAdQJD0t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646699\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}